msgid "guru"
msgstr "guru"

#: ../../G/guru.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../G/guru.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Unix] An expert. Implies not only :ref:`wizard` skill but also a history of"
" being a knowledge resource for others. Less often, used (with a qualifier) "
"for other experts on other systems, as in VMS guru. See :ref:`source-of-all-"
"good-bits`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Unix] 専門家。\\ :ref:`wizard`\\ "
"の技能だけでなく、他者にとって知識の拠り所であってきた歴史をも含意する。あまり多くはないが、(限定詞を付けて)他のシステムの他の専門家、たとえばVMS "
"guruのように使われる。\\ :ref:`source-of-all-good-bits`\\ を参照。"
